deaths_recoveries.notes: Died on 19th April. Was suffering from HTN.
Prominent Neuro surgeon of Chennai passed away at Apollo Hospital. Locals created ruckus and did not allow a proper burial fearing the disease.

The deceased who was suffering from Parkinson disease for the past three years was admitted to the hospital due to fever. His throat swab report arrived on Apr 20th night confirmed positive for coronavirus. He passed away in the morning of April 20th.
